Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是婴儿的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, when I was a baby,
