Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来简单  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"It looked easy, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Oh, what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-首先...  -妈  度假是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- "First, there..." - Mama, what's "vacation" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-度假  -爸爸去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Vacation? - Where Daddy went.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度假就是你去一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vacation's when you go somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再也不回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我想你可以说  我和妈妈只能靠自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, I guess you could say me and Mama was on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们不介意  我们的房子总是住满了人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we didn't mind. Our house was never empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是有人来来去去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was always folks coming and going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃晚饭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-吃晚饭了  各位  -天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's supper, everyone. - My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-弗里斯特  -看起来真特别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Forrest... - That sure looks special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候住在我们家的人太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes we had so many people staying with us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个房间都挤满了旅行者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that every room was filled with travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那些  靠行李箱和帽箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, folks living out of their suitcases
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和样品箱生活的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and hat cases and sample cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特·甘  吃晚饭了  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest Gump, it's suppertime! Forrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次  一个年轻人住在我们家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One time, a young man was staying with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带着一个吉他箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he had him a guitar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我跟你说了别打扰这个好心的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest! I told you not to bother this nice young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, that's all right, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是给他展示一下吉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was just showing him a thing or two on the guitar here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  如果你们想吃晚饭的话  已经准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, but your supper's ready if y'all want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  听起来不错  谢谢  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that sounds good. Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小家伙  再给我看看你刚刚那个疯狂的步伐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, man, show me that crazy little walk you just did there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微慢一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Slow it down some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢那把吉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I liked that guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sounded good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始随着音乐移动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I started moving around to the music,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆动我的臀部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}swinging my hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天晚上  我和妈妈出去买东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This one night, me and Mama was out shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们路过本森家居用品店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we walked right by Benson's furniture and appliance store,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是给孩子看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is not for children's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年后  那个英俊的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some years later, that handsome young man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是被称为"猫王"的那个传奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who they called "The King,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他唱了太多的歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}well, he'd sung too many songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏病发作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}had himself a heart attack, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当王一定很辛苦吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Must be hard being a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的是你记得一些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it's funny how you remember some things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有些事情却记不起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but some things you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要全力以赴  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You do your very best now, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sure will, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚地记得开学第一天乘校车的情景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember the bus ride on the first day of school very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要不要上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说不要搭陌生人的车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama said not to be taking rides from strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是去学校的校车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the bus to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫弗里斯特  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Forrest. Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫多洛希·哈里斯  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Dorothy Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们不是陌生人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, now we ain't strangers anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个座位有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This seat's taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能坐在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子的记忆很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it's funny what a young man recollects,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不记得我是怎么出生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause I don't remember being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得我在第一个圣诞节收到了什么礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't recall what I got for my first Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不记得我第一次去野餐是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I don't know when I went on my first outdoor picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我清楚地记得第一次听到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I do remember the first time I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个世界上最甜美的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the sweetest voice in the wide world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意  可以坐在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can sit here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一生中从未见过如此美丽的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had never seen anything so beautiful in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就像一个天使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底坐不坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, are you gonna sit down, or aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腿怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's wrong with your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  谢谢关心  我的腿好得很\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing at all, thank you. My legs are just fine and dandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在校车上  我坐在她身旁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just sat next to her on that bus
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她一路聊到学校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and had a conversation all the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脊背像问号一样弯曲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...my back's crooked like a question mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些支架会让我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These are going to make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我妈  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And next to Mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有人和我说过话或者问我问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}no one ever talked to me or asked me questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是傻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说  "只有做傻事的才是傻子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama says, "Stupid is as stupid does."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我叫珍妮  -我叫弗里斯特  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm Jenny. - I'm Forrest. Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起  我们总是在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From that day on, we was always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮和我形影不离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny and me was like peas and carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她教我怎么爬树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She taught me how to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  弗里斯特  你能行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Forrest, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教她怎么悬挂摇晃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I showed her how to dangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直乖巧的小猴子和...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"A good little monkey and..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她帮助我识字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She helped me learn how to read,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教她怎么倒挂金钩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I showed her how to swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我们只是坐在外面  等着看星星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes we'd just sit out and wait for the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈会担心我的 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama's gonna worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下再多待一会儿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为什么  珍妮从来不想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For some reason, Jenny didn't never want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  珍妮  我留下陪你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Jenny, I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我最特别的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was my most special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈总是跟我说  奇迹每天都会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, my mama always told me that miracles happen every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人不这么认为  但是确实如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some people don't think so, but they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是弱智  还是傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you retarded, or just plain stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"看啊  我是弗里斯特·瘸子" \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Look, I'm Forrest Gimp."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just run away, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  快跑  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest! Run away! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-骑车追  -快点  我们去抓他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get the bikes! - Hurry up! Let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快点  -小心  笨蛋  我们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Come on! - Look out, dummy, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会抓到你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  快跑  弗里斯特  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest, run! Run, Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我告诉你  你也不会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, you wouldn't believe it if I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可以跑得像风一样快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I can run like the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起  如果我要去什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From that day on, if I was going somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就跑着去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要跑了  拦住他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's getting away! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真是个跑得快的傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That boy sure is a running fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我跟你说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, remember how I told you that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮似乎从来不想回家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny never seemed to want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她住的房子有阿拉巴马州那么古老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, she lived in a house that was as old as Alabama.
