Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个很有爱心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was a very loving man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总是在亲吻抚摸珍妮和她的姐妹们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was always kissing and touching her and her sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有一次  珍妮没有坐校车去上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then this one time, Jenny wasn't on the bus to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮  你今天怎么没去上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny, why didn't you come to school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸正在午睡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Daddy's taking a nap.
