Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我回来  死丫头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd better get back here, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑到哪儿去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮  珍妮  你在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny! Jenny! Where you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起祈祷  弗里斯特  和我一起祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pray with me, Forrest. Pray with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的上帝  把我变成一只鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear God, make me a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就能逃离这里  远走高飞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I can fly far, far, far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的上帝  把我变成一只鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear God, make me a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就能逃离这里  远走高飞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I can fly far, far, far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈总说上帝是神秘的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama always said that God is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天祂没有把珍妮变成一只鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't turn Jenny into a bird that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好给我赶快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd better get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祂叫来了警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he had the police say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说珍妮再也不用住在那个房子里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny didn't have to stay in that house no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她搬去和她外婆住了  就住在克里克莫尔大道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She went to live with her grandma just over on Creekmore Avenue,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心  因为这样她就离我家很近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which made me happy, 'cause she was so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮有时晚上会偷偷溜到我家来玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some nights, Jenny would sneak out and come on over to my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为她说自己害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just 'cause she said she was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道她害怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Scared of what, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得是害怕她外婆的狗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I think it was her grandma's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只恶犬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was a mean dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  我和珍妮直到高中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, Jenny and me was best friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all the way up through high school.
