Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  弗里斯特  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到我说的话吗  蠢蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you hear me, stupid?
