Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车  快追\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get in the truck! Let's move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  他要逃了  开车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, he's getting away! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  弗里斯特  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest! Run!
