Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲冲冲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前都是跑到哪里是哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, it used to be, I ran to get where I was going,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过自己竟然会跑出名堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never thought it would take me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他妈是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who in the hell is that?
