Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是这世上最蠢的白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He must be the stupidest son of a bitch alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他是真的快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he sure is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来  或许只有我这么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, maybe it's just me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大学时光真的很迷茫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but college was very confusing times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天联邦政府派遣军队强制执行法院命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Federal troops enforcing a court order
