Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两名黑人学生获准入学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two negroes were admitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但乔治·华莱士州长随后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but only after Governor George Wallace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出象征性威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}had carried out his symbolic threat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡在了学校大楼门口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to stand in the school house door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华莱士州长  那个声明上说...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Governor Wallace, I take it from that statement, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厄尔 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Earl,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what's going on?
