Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果浣熊想进我家后院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When raccoons try to get on our back porch,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:22:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈就会用扫帚赶走它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama just chase them off with a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的浣熊  你个白痴  是黑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not raccoons, you idiot, niggers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想和我们一起上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they want to go to school with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们同校  当真吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With us? They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华莱士州长履行承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shortly after Governor Wallace had carried out his promise
