Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用武力干预\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then to use military force.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本台播放的录像记录了当时国民警卫队指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here, by videotape, is the encounter by General Graham,
