Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是阿甘吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, wasn't that Gump?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不可能 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nah, that couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sure as hell was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年后  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个生气地挡在学校大楼门口的小男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that angry little man at the school house door
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得竞选总统会是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thought it would be a good idea and ran for president.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有人觉得这不是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But somebody thought that it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他没死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的公交车到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My bus is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是9路车吗  -不  是4路车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is it the number nine? - No, it's the number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.87,0:24:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴和你聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得当时华莱士遇刺的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember when that happened, when Wallace got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.04,0:25:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在上大学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上的是女校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you go to a girls' college,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.75,0:25:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是男女混校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or to a girls-and-boys-together college?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.79,0:25:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女混校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was co-ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.78,0:25:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮上的大学我就不能去上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause Jenny went to a college I couldn't go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.63,0:25:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大学只收女生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a college just for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.10,0:25:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一有机会就会去看她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I'd go and visit her every chance I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.26,0:25:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest! Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.84,0:26:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  住手  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在伤害你  -这他妈是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He was hurting you. - What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.77,0:26:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  他没有  去那边  -他是谁  他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, he's not! Get over there! - Who is that? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.70,0:26:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-比利  对不起  -什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Billy, I'm sorry. - What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.65,0:26:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-离我远点  -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just get away from me! - Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.50,0:26:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不要走  比利  等等  -离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Don't go! Billy, wait a second! - Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.49,0:26:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全不懂事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He doesn't know any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.44,0:26:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你为什么要那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.10,0:26:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带了点巧克力来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I brought you some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.28,0:26:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.31,0:26:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我现在就回学校了  -弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll go back to my college now. - Forrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.32,0:26:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你这样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.90,0:26:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.71,0:26:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的寝室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.90,0:27:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你是否会梦想着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you ever dream, Forrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.43,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想成为什么样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about who you're gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.40,0:27:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要成为什么样的人  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Who I'm gonna be? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.12,0:27:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我不再是我自己了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aren't I going to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.17,0:27:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远都会是你  只是你还有其他可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you'll always be you, just another kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.76,0:27:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.82,0:27:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想出名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to be famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为像琼·贝兹一样的歌手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to be a singer like Joan Baez.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.71,0:27:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想站在空旷的舞台上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want to be on an empty stage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.03,0:27:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里只有我的吉他和歌声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with my guitar, my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.11,0:27:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.00,0:27:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想触动人们的内心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I want to reach people on the personal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.07,0:27:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拥有与人一对一交心的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to be able to say things, just one-to-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.92,0:27:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和女孩在一起过吗  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever been with a girl, Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.20,0:28:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上家政课的时候一直和她们坐在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sit next to them in my Home Economics class all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.25,0:28:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对不起  -没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm... Sorry. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.05,0:28:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事的  -我头晕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's okay. - Oh, I'm dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.41,0:29:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你在家政课上没做过这个吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bet that never happened in Home Ec.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.94,0:29:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我弄脏了你舍友的浴袍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I ruined your roommate's bathrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.61,0:29:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  反正我也不喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care. I don't like her, anyway.
