Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.58,0:29:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学生活过得飞快 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}College ran by real fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.34,0:29:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我参加太多橄榄球比赛了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause I played so much football.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.90,0:29:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还把我弄进了全美明星队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They even put me on a thing called the All-America Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.46,0:29:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(205.2,78.933)}{\fn方正胖娃_GBK\fs25\b0\bord1\shad7\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HB3C1B8&\4c&H211F24&}派拉蒙新闻报道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.17,0:29:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去后可以见到美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where you get to meet the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.08,0:29:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯尼迪总统今天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}President Kennedy met with
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在白宫办公室接见了全美大学生橄榄球队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Collegiate All-American Football Team at the Oval Office today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.97,0:29:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会见美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, the really good thing about meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.97,0:29:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的好处就是有好吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the President of the United States is the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.94,0:30:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会安排你坐在一个小厅里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They put you in this little room
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.67,0:30:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面吃的喝的都应有尽有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with just about anything you'd want to eat or drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.54,0:30:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  第一  我不饿  但是渴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And since, number one, I wasn't hungry, but thirsty,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.26,0:30:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  饮料是免费的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and number two, they was free,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.02,0:30:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概喝了15瓶汽水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I must have drank me about 15 Dr. Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.95,0:30:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  入选全美明星队感觉如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations. How does it feel to be an All-American?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.34,0:30:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's an honor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.01,0:30:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  入选全美明星队感觉如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations. How does it feel to be an All-American?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.24,0:30:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.74,0:30:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  入选全美明星队感觉如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations. How does it feel to be an All-American?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.24,0:30:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.07,0:30:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-恭喜  你感觉如何  -我想尿尿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Congratulations. How do you feel? - I gotta pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.66,0:30:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像听到他说他要尿尿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe he said he had to "Go pee."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.93,0:30:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后  莫名其妙地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometime later, for no particular reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.76,0:30:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人枪杀了这位年轻的好总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}somebody shot that nice young President,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.30,0:30:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他正坐在车里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when he was riding in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.35,0:31:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了几年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a few years after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.57,0:31:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有人枪杀了他的弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}somebody shot his little brother, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.69,0:31:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过他当时是在酒店厨房里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}only he was in a hotel kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.19,0:31:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做兄弟也太难了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It must be hard being brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.81,0:31:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反正没机会体会这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.41,0:31:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.84,0:31:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢相信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.29,0:31:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过玩了五年橄榄球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After only five years of playing football,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.52,0:31:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然拿到了大学学位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got a college degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.26,0:31:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.07,0:31:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈骄傲极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama was so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.42,0:31:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我太为你骄傲了  我帮你拿这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, I'm so proud of you. Here, I'll hold this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.61,0:31:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对自己的未来有没有什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you given any thought to your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.46,0:31:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.62,0:31:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(324.8,185.6)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs15\b1\bord1\blur4\shad0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H815436&}青年才俊\N踊跃参军
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.15,0:31:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是弗里斯特  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, I'm Forrest. Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.30,0:31:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在乎你他妈是什么狗东西  混球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody gives a hunk of shit who you are, fuzzball!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.27,0:31:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连低等生物都不如  吃屎的蛆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not even a low-life, scum-sucking maggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.00,0:31:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚去你的座位上  你现在是在军队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get your faggotty ass on the bus. You're in the Army now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.23,0:31:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个座位有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This seat's taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.06,0:31:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.26,0:32:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始  我觉得自己做了个错误的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At first, it seemed like I made a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为入伍的第一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}seeing how it was only my induction day
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.12,0:32:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就被人无情地怒吼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I was already getting yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意  可以坐在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can sit down if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.42,0:32:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道自己会遇到什么人  或者被问什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't know who I might meet, or what they might ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.43,0:32:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有乘过真正的捕虾船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ever been on a real shrimp boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  但我乘过很大的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, but I been on a real big boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.90,0:32:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是一种专门捕虾的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm talking about a shrimp-catching boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一辈子都在捕虾船上干活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been working on shrimp boats all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.36,0:32:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始是在我舅舅的船上  就是我妈妈的弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I started out on my uncle's boat, that's my mama's brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.39,0:32:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我可能大概9岁吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I was about maybe nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.47,0:32:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想买一艘自己的船  然后却被强制入伍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was just looking into buying a boat of my own and got drafted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.34,0:32:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是本杰明·巴福德·布鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My given name is Benjamin Buford Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.87,0:32:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都叫我巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People call me Bubba.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.95,0:32:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以前南方佬常用的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like one of them old redneck boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.14,0:32:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是弗里斯特·甘 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My name's Forrest Gump. 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.83,0:32:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫我弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People call me Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.27,0:32:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴来自阿拉巴马州的拜尤拉巴特里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, Bubba was from Bayou La Batre, Alabama,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.86,0:32:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈妈是煮虾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and his mama cooked shrimp,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.96,0:33:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的外婆也是煮虾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and her mama before her cooked shrimp,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.00,0:33:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的外曾祖母也是煮虾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and her mama before her mama cooked shrimp, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.04,0:33:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴的家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba's family
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.85,0:33:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对整个虾行业都知道得一清二楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}knew everything there was to know about the shrimping business.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.04,0:33:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对整个虾行业都知道得一清二楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know everything there is to know about the shrimping business.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  我打算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Matter of fact, I'm going into
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.45,0:33:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等退伍之后  也投身虾行业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the shrimping business for myself after I get out the Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.56,0:33:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘  你是为了什么来参军的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gump! What's your sole purpose in this Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.74,0:33:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成你下达的任何指令  德尔中士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To do whatever you tell me, Drill Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.34,0:33:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的  阿甘  你真他妈是个天才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God damn it, Gump! You're a goddamn genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我听过的最优秀的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the most outstanding answer I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.26,0:33:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的智商一定有他们的160分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You must have a goddamn IQ of 160!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.12,0:33:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真他妈有天赋  二等兵甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are goddamn gifted, Private Gump!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.21,0:33:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体都听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen up, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.07,0:33:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.00,0:33:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在军队里混得如鱼得水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fit in the Army like one of them round pegs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.33,0:33:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的并不难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.83,0:33:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只需把床铺得很整齐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just make your bed real neat
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.52,0:33:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得站直\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and remember to stand up straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.52,0:33:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且总是用"是  德尔中士"来回答所有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and always answer every question with, "Yes, Drill Sergeant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.65,0:33:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.02,0:34:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  德尔中士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Drill Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.86,0:34:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只需要贴着海底拖渔网\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What you do is, you just drag your nets along the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.13,0:34:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运气好的话  你一次就能捕到100多磅的虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On a good day, you can catch over 100 pounds of shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.92,0:34:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一切顺利的话  两个人捕虾十个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If everything goes all right, two men shrimping 10 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再减去油费  就能...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}less what you spend on gas, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.21,0:34:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装完了  德尔中士 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Done, Drill Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.02,0:34:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gump!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.37,0:34:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么组装枪这么快  阿甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did you put that weapon together so quickly, Gump?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.37,0:34:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我这么做的  德尔中士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You told me to, Drill Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.09,0:34:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的上帝  你创了本连的新纪录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus H. Christ, this is a new company record.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.63,0:34:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是担心浪费了这么好的一个兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If it wouldn't be a waste of such a damn fine enlisted man,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想推荐你去候补军官学校  二等兵甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd recommend you for OCS, Private Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将来一定能成为一名将军  阿甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are gonna be a general some day, Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.41,0:34:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在拆开你的枪  重新组装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, disassemble your weapon and continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.51,0:34:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我刚刚说过的  虾就是大海结出的果实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, like I was saying, shrimp is the fruit of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.59,0:34:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以做烤虾  水煮虾  炒虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can barbecue it, boil it, broil it, bake it, sauté it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做烤虾串  克里奥尔烩虾...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's shrimp kebabs, shrimp Creole...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虾浓汤  平锅煎虾  油炸虾  清炒虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...shrimp gumbo, pan fried, deep fried, stir fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.94,0:35:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有菠萝虾  柠檬虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's pineapple shrimp, lemon shrimp,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.46,0:35:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子虾  胡椒虾...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}coconut shrimp, pepper shrimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.06,0:35:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜虾汤  烩虾  鲜虾沙拉  虾肉炖土豆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...shrimp soup, shrimp stew, shrimp salad, shrimp and potatoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虾肉汉堡  鲜虾三明治...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}shrimp burger, shrimp sandwich...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.82,0:35:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差...差不多就这些了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's... That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.95,0:35:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队里的夜晚格外孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Night time in the Army is a lonely time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.78,0:35:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会躺在床铺上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd lay there in our bunks
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.01,0:35:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想念我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'd miss my mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.95,0:35:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会想念珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'd miss Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.60,0:35:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gump,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看看她的胸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get a load of the tits on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.62,0:35:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发现  珍妮惹上了一些麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turns out, Jenny had gotten into some trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.84,0:36:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她穿着校服拍了几张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over some photos of her in her college sweater,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她被学校开除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she was thrown out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.46,0:36:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也并非一件坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that wasn't a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.82,0:36:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一个在田纳西州孟菲斯有剧场的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because a man who owns a theater in Memphis, Tennessee,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.38,0:36:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了那些照片 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}saw those photos
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.11,0:36:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给珍妮提供了一份登台唱歌的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and offered Jenny a job singing in a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.33,0:36:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一有机会休假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The first chance I got,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.21,0:36:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就马上乘大巴去孟菲斯  去看她的表演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took the bus up to Memphis to see her perform in that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.02,0:36:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚表演的是安波  安波·弗莱姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was Amber, Amber Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.39,0:36:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家为她热烈鼓掌  好样的  安波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give her a big hand, guys. Good job, Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.16,0:36:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  为您带来视听双重享受的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now, for your listening and viewing pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.88,0:36:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自加州好莱坞的  我们跨掉一代的美人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}direct from Hollywood, California, our very own beatnik beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.78,0:36:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们热烈欢迎性感的芭比·迪伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}let's give a big round of applause to the luscious Bobbi Dylan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.65,0:36:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好极了  -芭比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right! - Bobbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.90,0:36:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪一个男人要走过多少路♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪How many roads must a man walk down♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪才能称为真正的男人♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪Before you can call him a man♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.33,0:37:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪一只白鸽要飞越过多少片大海♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪How many seas must a white dove sail♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.68,0:37:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪才能在沙滩上安睡♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪Before she sleeps in the sand♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.92,0:37:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的梦想已经成真了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Her dream had come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.29,0:37:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她成了民谣歌手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was a folk singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.43,0:37:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪炮弹要多少次掠过天空♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪How many times must the cannon balls fly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.93,0:37:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪才能永远被废止♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪Before they're forever banned♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来呀  宝贝  扭起来  抖起来嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, baby. Shake it up. Shake it up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.95,0:37:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  伙计  给她换个口琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, buddy, get her a harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.13,0:37:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪我的朋友啊  这些问题的答案在风中飘扬♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪The answer, my friend, is blowin' in the wind♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.61,0:37:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  甜心  这可不是《袋鼠船长》{\fs12}[儿童节目]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, honey, this ain't Captain Kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  甜心  我有东西要送给你哦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, honey, I got something here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.04,0:37:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.93,0:37:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个蠢货混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.75,0:37:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这唱着歌呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm singing a song here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.54,0:37:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波利  滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Polly, get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.00,0:37:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-闭嘴  滚  -别害羞嘛  甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Shut up, there! - Don't be so shy, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.67,0:37:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.15,0:37:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你在这干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.85,0:37:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-拜托  -你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Come on. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.22,0:37:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  放下我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.02,0:38:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能一直这样做  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't keep doing this, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.88,0:38:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能一直试图来拯救我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't keep trying to rescue me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.18,0:38:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们刚刚想摸你  -很多人都想摸我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- They was trying to grab you. - A lot of people try to grab me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.92,0:38:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但...你不能一直这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just... You can't keep doing this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.01,0:38:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我控制不了  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.16,0:38:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.75,0:38:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你根本不知道什么是爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, you don't know what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得那次我们祷告吗  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You remember that time we prayed, Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.49,0:38:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们向上帝祷告  希望祂能把我变成一只鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We prayed for God to turn me into a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.72,0:38:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就可以飞走了  飞得远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I could fly far, far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.03,0:38:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.33,0:38:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我能飞下这座大桥吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think I could fly off this bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.79,0:39:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean, Jenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.88,0:39:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.29,0:39:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.56,0:39:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait, Jenny...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.83,0:39:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你离我远点  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, you stay away from me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.45,0:39:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just stay away from me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.38,0:39:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能搭个顺风车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I have a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要去哪儿  -随便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where you going? - I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, bye-bye, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.20,0:39:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要派我去越南\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They sending me to Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.25,0:39:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是另外一个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's this whole other country.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.22,0:39:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.56,0:39:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  你要向我保证一件事  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, you promise me something, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.65,0:39:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一你碰到危险  不要逞强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just, if you're ever in trouble, don't try to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.67,0:39:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只管跑  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just run, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.07,0:39:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑得远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.97,0:39:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.22,0:39:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.35,0:40:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直给你写信的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll write you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.83,0:40:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样  她上车走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And just like that, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.01,0:40:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要平安回来  听见了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You come back safe to me, do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.55,0:41:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们告诉我们在越南和在美国服役相比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, they told us that Vietnam was gonna be very different
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.62,0:41:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会完全不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.84,0:41:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但除了成箱的啤酒和野外烧烤外  的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And except for all the beer cans and the barbecue, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜这片水域里一定有虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bet there's shrimp all in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.96,0:41:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟我说这些越南人都很会捕虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They tell me these Vietnams is good shrimpers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.31,0:41:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们打赢了仗  我们就能接管一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, after we win this war, and we take over everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.81,0:41:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能让美国的捕虾者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can get American shrimpers
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里  在这片水域里捕虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to come out here and shrimp these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.00,0:41:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要一直捕虾就好了 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll just shrimp all the time, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多很多的虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So much shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.43,0:41:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一定是我的新兵吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You must be my FNGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.62,0:42:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早安  长官  -早安  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Morning, sir! - Morning, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.75,0:42:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放下  别向我行礼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get your hands down! Do not salute me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.59,0:42:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近有很多该死的狙击手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's goddamn snipers all around this area
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.73,0:42:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢射杀军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who would love to grease an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.66,0:42:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是丹·泰勒中尉  欢迎来到四排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Lieutenant Dan Taylor. Welcome to Fourth Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.09,0:42:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的嘴唇怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's wrong with your lip?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.63,0:42:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我天生嘴唇厚  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was born with big gums, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.05,0:42:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那你最好把嘴唇吸回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, you better tuck that in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.22,0:42:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然容易碰到地雷线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gonna get that caught on a trip wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.93,0:42:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个老家都是哪里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where you boys from in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.36,0:42:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-阿拉巴马州  长官  -阿拉巴马州  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Alabama, sir! - Alabama, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.49,0:42:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是双胞胎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.11,0:42:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我们没有血缘关系  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, we are not relations, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.75,0:42:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  这边规矩很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, it's pretty basic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.51,0:42:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你们跟着我  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you stick with me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.18,0:42:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向在这里待了一段时间的老兵好好学习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and learn from the guys who've been in country a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.76,0:42:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一样必备的军需品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is one item of GI gear
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.49,0:42:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它将关系到你们的生死存亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that can be the difference between a live grunt and a dead grunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.21,0:42:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是袜子  底部有衬垫  绿色的袜子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Socks. Cushion sole, OD green.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.49,0:42:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量保持双脚干燥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Try and keep your feet dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.88,0:42:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们负重出行的时候  你们一定要记住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When we're out humping, I want you boys to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.34,0:43:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要停下休整  就要换干爽的袜子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to change your socks whenever we stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.98,0:43:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然湄公河会泡烂你的脚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Mekong will eat a grunt's feet right off his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.03,0:43:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希姆斯中士  该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sergeant Sims, God damn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.30,0:43:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你申报的吊索在哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where is that sling rope I told you to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.76,0:43:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经写在军队的申请单上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I put in the requisitions at Battalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.78,0:43:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧  那你再给那群混蛋打电话...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, yeah, yeah, well, you call those sons of bitches again...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.90,0:43:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉对军队的事务十分熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan sure knew his stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.52,0:43:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能做我的中尉  我真是太幸运了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I felt real lucky he was my lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.64,0:43:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出身于战功显赫的军人世家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was from a long, great military tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.31,0:43:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国历史上的每一场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody in his family had fought and died
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.36,0:43:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的家人都曾参与并战死其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in every single American war.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.57,0:43:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-该死的  使劲催  -马上去办  中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- God damn it, kick some ass! - I'm on it, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.60,0:43:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.79,0:43:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许可以说  他要达到祖辈的丰功伟绩需要艰苦奋斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess you could say he had a lot to live up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.84,0:43:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们都是来自阿肯色州的  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, you boys are from Arkansas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.15,0:43:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去过那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.86,0:43:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小石城是个好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Little Rock's a fine town.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.70,0:43:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放下你们的装备  去找排长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, go shake down your gear, see the platoon sergeant,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领你们上阵需要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}draw what you need for the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.07,0:43:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们饿了  那边正烤着牛排呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you boys are hungry, we got steaks burning right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.04,0:43:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本排有两条守则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two standing orders in this platoon:
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.03,0:44:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  照顾好你的脚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one, take good care of your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.71,0:44:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二  不要干蠢事  比如害死自己之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}two, try not to do anything stupid, like getting yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望我不会让他失望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sure hope I don't let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.88,0:44:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以经常看到乡下的风光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got to see a lot of the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.75,0:44:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们经常会走很长的路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We would take these real long walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在找一个叫查理{\fs12}[越共]{\fs}的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we were always looking for this guy named Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.40,0:44:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-停下  -停下  各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hold it up! - Hold up, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.28,0:45:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并非一直是快乐有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It wasn't always fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.74,0:45:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉总是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan was always
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.35,0:45:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会对路上的风吹草动有着古怪的直觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}getting these funny feelings about a rock, or a trail, or the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.37,0:45:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会叫我们趴下  闭嘴...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so he'd tell us to get down, shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.28,0:45:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下  闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get down! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.33,0:45:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们照做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...so we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.36,0:45:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我对所有事情都不太懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I don't know much about anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.79,0:45:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得美国一批最出色的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I think some of America's best young men
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.85,0:45:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都投入到了这场战争中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}served in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.52,0:45:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如  来自凤凰城的达拉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was Dallas, from Phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.81,0:45:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自底特律的克利夫兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cleveland, he was from Detroit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.00,0:45:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰克斯  泰克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tex. Hey, Tex.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.57,0:45:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面到底怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man, what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰克斯来自...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Tex was...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.66,0:45:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得泰克斯来自哪里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I don't remember where Tex come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.58,0:45:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.65,0:46:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四排  起立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fourth Platoon, on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.22,0:46:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离那条河还有十公里  出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Still got 10 klicks to go to that river. Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.15,0:46:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.96,0:46:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟上  快点  打起精神来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Step it up. Look alive out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在越南最好的一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The good thing about Vietnam
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.36,0:46:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是总会有地方可去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is there was always some place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.91,0:46:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心手雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.68,0:46:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘  检查一下那个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gump, check out that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.45,0:46:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也总是有事可做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And there was always something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.36,0:46:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跟上  -散开  掩护他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mount them up. - Spread out! Cover his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天  突然开始下雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One day, it started raining,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.10,0:46:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整整下了四个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it didn't quit for four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.98,0:46:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们经历了各种各样的雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd been through every kind of rain there is:
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.93,0:46:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的淅沥沥的雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}little bitty stinging rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.30,0:46:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大大的哗啦啦的雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and big old fat rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.44,0:46:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴着狂风的暴雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}rain that flew in sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候  雨甚至像是从地下冒上来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And sometimes, rain even seemed to come straight up from underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.09,0:47:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  连晚上也下雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shoot, it even rained at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.49,0:47:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嘿  弗里斯特  -你好  巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, Forrest. - Hey, Bubba.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.97,0:47:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要靠在你身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna lean up against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.29,0:47:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也靠在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just lean right back against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.48,0:47:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  我们的头就不用枕在泥里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This way, we don't have to sleep with our heads in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.22,0:47:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么我们是一对好搭档吗  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know why we a good partnership, Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.77,0:47:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们会互相关照彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause we be watching out for one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.37,0:47:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像兄弟一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like brothers and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.47,0:47:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我一直在想一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, there's something I've been thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.98,0:47:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个非常重要的问题要问你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got a very important question to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.57,0:47:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想跟我一起做捕虾的行当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How would you like to go into the shrimping business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.83,0:47:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.37,0:47:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你  我也全都想清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man, I tell you what, I got it all figured out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.99,0:47:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要捕多少磅虾才能付清买船的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So many pounds of shrimp to pay off the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.81,0:47:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕多少磅虾付油钱  我们可以直接住在船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so many pounds for gas, we can just live right on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.34,0:47:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就不用交房租了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We ain't got to pay no rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.57,0:47:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当船长  我们可以合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be the captain, we can just work it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.95,0:47:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有收入对半分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}split everything right down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.85,0:47:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你  一人一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man, I'm telling you, 50-50.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.14,0:48:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你想吃多少虾都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, hey, Forrest, all the shrimp you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a fine idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.13,0:48:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴确实想出了个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba did have a fine idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.09,0:48:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至写信给珍妮  把这事告诉了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I even wrote Jenny and told her all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.94,0:48:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常给她写信  虽不是每天都写  但也差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sent her letters, not every day, but almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.33,0:48:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉她我在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told her what I was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.62,0:48:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问她都在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and asked her what she was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.46,0:48:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉她我一直以来有多想她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and told her how I thought about her always,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.51,0:48:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我有多么期盼收到她的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and how I was looking forward to getting a letter from her
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.66,0:48:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是她有时间回信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just as soon as she had the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.89,0:48:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是让她知道我平安无事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd always let her know that I was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.73,0:48:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在每封信的落款  我会写上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then, I'd sign each letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.31,0:48:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"爱你的  弗里斯特·甘"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Love, Forrest Gump."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.83,0:49:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天  我们走在外面  就像平常一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This one day, we was out walking, like always,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.55,0:49:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then, just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.39,0:49:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有人把雨关停了  太阳出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}somebody turned off the rain and the sun come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.81,0:49:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.21,0:49:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.12,0:49:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.89,0:49:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿M60机枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get the sixty!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.12,0:49:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把机关枪拿过来  该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get that pig up here, God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.37,0:49:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.55,0:49:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁腕  铁腕  请注意  铁腕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Strongarm! Strongarm! Be advised, Strongarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.86,0:49:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医务兵  这边有一个人受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Medic, we got a man down!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.37,0:49:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁腕  这里是利马腿6号小队  完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Strongarm, this is Leg Lima 6, over!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.91,0:49:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  铁腕 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roger, Strongarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.18,0:49:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}be advised
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.92,0:49:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在「B+2」地点的林木线附近遭遇敌袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we have incoming from the tree line at point blue plus two.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.51,0:49:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有AK步枪和火箭弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}AKs and rockets...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.80,0:49:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪射不出  无法射击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Misfire! Misfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.75,0:49:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的  麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God damn it! Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.66,0:50:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那玩意儿...  操  先进森林里去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get that thing... Fuck it, get it in the tree line!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.34,0:50:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小队遭受重创\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My unit is down hard and hurting!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.75,0:50:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6号小队撤退回蓝线  利马腿6号结束通话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Six are pulling back to Blue Line, Leg Lima 6 out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.96,0:50:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pull back! Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.39,0:50:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  快跑  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run! Run, Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.35,0:50:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-撤退  -弗里斯特  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Pull back! - Forrest, Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.80,0:50:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  兄弟  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, man! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.52,0:50:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pull back! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.10,0:50:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  该死的  快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run, God damn it, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.33,0:50:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医务兵  有医务兵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Medic! Can I get a medic?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.51,0:50:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑啊跑  就像珍妮叫我做的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ran and ran, just like Jenny told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.33,0:51:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑得太远太快  很快就只剩下我独自一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ran so far and so fast that pretty soon I was all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.47,0:51:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不太妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which was a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.94,0:51:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.55,0:51:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴是我最亲最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba was my best good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.00,0:51:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得确保他平安无事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to make sure that he was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.01,0:51:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有自己人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any friendlies out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.15,0:51:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  我这里有三个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I've got three over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.05,0:51:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.60,0:51:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.91,0:51:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我回去找巴巴的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And on my way back to find Bubba,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.78,0:51:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现了一个男孩躺在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}well, there was this boy laying on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.71,0:51:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tex!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.98,0:51:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.98,0:51:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能任由他一个人躺在那里 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't just let him lay there all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.03,0:51:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他惊魂未定  极度恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}scared the way he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.11,0:51:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我扛起他  带他跑了出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I grabbed him up and run him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.12,0:52:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我回去找巴巴时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And every time I went back looking for Bubba,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.63,0:52:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有别人在喊  "救救我  弗里斯特  救救我"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}somebody else was saying, "Help me, Forrest. Help me."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.89,0:52:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见  听不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't hear... Can't hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.13,0:52:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  兄弟  躺着就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No sweat, man. Just lay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.42,0:52:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会没事的  你会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll be okay. You'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.84,0:52:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我渐渐开始害怕我可能永远也找不到巴巴了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I started to get scared that I might never find Bubba.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.37,0:52:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Over.
