Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.51,1:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个婴儿杀手是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's the baby killer?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.49,1:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我跟你提过的那个好朋友  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my good friend I told you about. This is Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.28,1:08:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  这是韦斯利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, this is Wesley.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.10,1:08:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦斯利和我一起住在伯克利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wesley and I lived together in Berkeley,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.58,1:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是学生民主协会伯克利分会的会长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he's the president of the Berkeley chapter of SDS.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.26,1:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再跟你说说其他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me tell you something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.77,1:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了向所有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are here to offer protection
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.43,1:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我们帮助的人  提供保护和帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and help for all of those who need our help,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.07,1:08:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们  黑豹党  反对越战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because we, the Black Panthers, are against the war in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.73,1:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们反对任何战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we are against any war
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.48,1:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些战争中  黑人士兵被送往前线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where black soldiers are sent to the frontline
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.47,1:08:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为一个憎恶他们的国家牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to die for a country that hates them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.55,1:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们反对任何黑人士兵参与的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we are against any war where black soldiers go to fight
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.86,1:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他们晚上睡觉时  在自己的社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and come to be brutalized and killed in their own communities
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.96,1:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被残害  被杀害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as they sleep in their beds at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.63,1:08:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们反对一切种族主义和帝国狗行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we are against all these racist and imperial dog acts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.46,1:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  住手  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest! Quit it! Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.65,1:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.54,1:09:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手  停下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.07,1:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.35,1:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不该带你到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I shouldn't have brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.60,1:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早该知道这只会是些狗屁麻烦事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should have known it was just gonna be some bullshit hassle.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.42,1:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不该打你  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He should not be hitting you, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.88,1:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.36,1:09:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我在你的黑豹党派对中途打架了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry I had a fight in the middle of your Black Panther party.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.21,1:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是有意做这种事的  他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He doesn't mean it when he does things like this. He doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.71,1:09:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都不会伤害你  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would never hurt you, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.85,1:10:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不会  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you wouldn't, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.05,1:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想当你的男朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to be your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.14,1:10:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身制服是场经历  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That uniform is a trip, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.04,1:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着很帅气  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You look handsome in it. You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.22,1:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你猜怎么着  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You know what? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.76,1:10:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴我们在国家首都相聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad we were here together in our nation's capital.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.10,1:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, too, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.92,1:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮和我散步一整晚  只是聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We walked around all night, Jenny and me, just talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.59,1:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了她所有的旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She told me about all the traveling she'd done.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.00,1:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及她发现如何开拓自己的思维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how she'd discovered ways to expand her mind
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.54,1:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学会如何和谐生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and learn how to live in harmony,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.80,1:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是在西部的某个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which must be out west somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.40,1:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}珍·哈露
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.06,1:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她一路去到了加州\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause she made it all the way to California.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.23,1:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn迷你简细行楷}{\bord0\fs14}♪现在就试着去爱对方♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪Try to love one another right now♪
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.00,1:11:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想去旧金山吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anybody want to go to San Francisco?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.68,1:11:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我去  -好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll go. - Far out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.99,1:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们两个来说  这是非常特别的一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a very special night for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.77,1:11:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时盼着那一夜永不结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't want it to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.79,1:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}伯克利至华盛顿特区
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.72,1:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想你离开  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish you wouldn't go, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.00,1:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须离开  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.95,1:11:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.23,1:11:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态有些失控了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things got a little out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.00,1:11:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这场战争和那个满嘴胡话的混蛋约翰逊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just this war and that lying son of a bitch, Johnson!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.54,1:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会伤害你  你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would never hurt you, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.40,1:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是怎么想的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.91,1:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该回阿拉巴马州的绿弓县\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you should go home to Greenbow, Alabama!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.61,1:12:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我们的生活截然不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, we have very different lives, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.08,1:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你收下这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.99,1:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我不能要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, I can't keep this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.78,1:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能得到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.75,1:12:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是因为我照你说的做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just by doing what you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.08,1:12:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么对我这么好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you so good to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.80,1:12:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.28,1:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都是你的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll always be your girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.96,1:13:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样  她走了  又从我的生命中消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And just like that, she was gone, out of my life again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.22,1:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个人的一小步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's one small step for man,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.58,1:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是人类的一大步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one giant leap for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.07,1:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我又要回越南了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought I was going back to Vietnam,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.68,1:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们却认定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but instead, they decided
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.71,1:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我对抗共产党的最好方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the best way for me to fight the Communists
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.95,1:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打乒乓球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was to play Ping-Pong.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.72,1:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我加入了特别服务部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I was in the Special Services,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.04,1:13:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全国各地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}traveling around the country
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.39,1:13:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为所有受伤的退伍军人加油打气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cheering up all them wounded veterans
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.44,1:14:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并教他们怎么打乒乓球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and showing them how to play Ping-Pong.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.87,1:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打得太好了  以至于几年后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was so good that some years later
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.93,1:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队决定让我加入全美乒乓球队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Army decided that I should be on the All-American Ping-Pong team.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.22,1:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是近百万年来  大概可以这么说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were the first Americans to visit the land of China
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.60,1:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一批踏上中国大陆的美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in like a million years, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.33,1:14:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说世界和平就掌握在我们手中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody said world peace was in our hands,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.96,1:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只是打了乒乓球而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but all I did was play Ping-Pong.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.65,1:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我回家时  我成了全美名人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I got home, I was a national celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.34,1:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比袋鼠船长还有名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Famouser even than Captain Kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.99,1:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了  弗里斯特·甘  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here he is, Forrest Gump, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.16,1:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘先生  请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Gump, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.41,1:14:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特·甘  这是约翰·列侬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest Gump, John Lennon.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.32,1:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-欢迎回家  -你刚结束了令人震撼的中国行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Welcome home. - You had quite a trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.52,1:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能告诉我们  中国是什么样子的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you tell us, what was China like?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.14,1:14:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中国  人们几乎一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the land of China, people hardly got nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.44,1:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有财产吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No possessions?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.72,1:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中国  人们从不去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And in China, they never go to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.25,1:15:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有宗教信仰吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No religion, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.86,1:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-难以想象  -只要你肯尝试  其实很容易  迪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hard to imagine. - Well, it's easy if you try, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.03,1:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年后  那位来自英国的帅小伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some years later, that nice young man from England
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.38,1:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回家看他儿子的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was on his way home to see his little boy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.06,1:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他正在签名时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and was signing some autographs,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.19,1:15:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无缘无故地  有人射杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and for no particular reason at all, somebody shot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.00,1:15:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz1.396\pos(238.217,67.01)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HB0B5B2&}演播室观众入口
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.19,1:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给你颁发了国会荣誉勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They gave you the Congressional Medal of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.44,1:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, that's Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.20,1:15:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.03,1:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给你颁发了国会荣誉勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They gave you the Congressional Medal of Honor!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.27,1:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  长官  是给我颁发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir, they surely did.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.87,1:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们竟然给你  一个低能儿  一个白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They gave you, an imbecile, a moron
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.95,1:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个在电视上当着全国人民的面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who goes on television and makes a fool out of himself
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.22,1:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自出洋相的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in front of the whole damn country,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.24,1:16:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颁发了国会荣誉勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Congressional Medal of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.76,1:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.11,1:16:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then, that's just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.89,1:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我对此只想说一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, I just got one thing to say to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.26,1:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑美国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God damn bless America.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.86,1:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.40,1:16:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天呐  -丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, God! - Lieutenant Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.10,1:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉说他住在一个旅馆里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan said he was living in a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.87,1:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他没有腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And because he didn't have no legs,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.04,1:16:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他大部分时间都在锻炼手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he spent most of his time exercising his arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.97,1:16:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右转  右转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take a right. Take a right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.90,1:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  快点啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, already!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.72,1:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在纽约做什么  丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you do here in New York, Lieutenant Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.56,1:16:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我靠政府救济生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm living off the government tit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.99,1:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸干它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sucking it dry!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.40,1:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞎了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you blind?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.50,1:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我走路呢  -快走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm walking here! - Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.62,1:17:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  快  走走走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get out! Come on, go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.65,1:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和丹上尉一起庆祝了节日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I stayed with Lieutenant Dan and celebrated the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.99,1:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家这一年很棒  回家吧  上帝祝福你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have a great year. Hurry home and God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.40,1:17:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到耶稣了吗  阿甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you found Jesus yet, Gump?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.69,1:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道我应该要找祂啊  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't know I was supposed to be looking for him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.90,1:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退伍军人中心的那帮瘸子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all these cripples, down at the VA,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.30,1:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天就说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's all they ever talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.88,1:17:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶稣这  耶稣那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus this and Jesus that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.27,1:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有找到耶稣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have I found Jesus?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.29,1:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们甚至找了个牧师来和我谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They even had a priest come and talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.19,1:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说上帝在倾听  但我得自救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said God is listening, but I have to help myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.18,1:18:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么如果我诚心接受耶稣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How if I accept Jesus into my heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.58,1:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将和他在天堂并肩行走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll get to walk beside him in the kingdom of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.50,1:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见我说的话了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.67,1:18:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他在天堂并肩行走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Walk beside him in the kingdom of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.74,1:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给老子滚蛋去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, kiss my crippled ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.79,1:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝在倾听  一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God is listening? What a crock of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.96,1:18:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会上天堂的  丹上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to heaven, Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.77,1:18:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在你去之前  不如先去一趟街角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Before you go, why don't you get your ass down to the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.01,1:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再买瓶酒回来  -遵命  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- and get us another bottle of Ripple. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.97,1:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在大约在纽约45街的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are at approximately 45th Street
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.05,1:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特广场一号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in New York City at One Astor Plaza.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.85,1:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是阿斯特酒店旧址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the site of the old Astor Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.63,1:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜尤拉巴特里到底有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell is in Bayou La Batre?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.11,1:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-捕虾船  -捕虾船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Shrimping boats. - Shrimping boats?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.50,1:19:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁他妈在乎捕虾船啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who gives a shit about shrimping boats?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.02,1:19:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我有钱  就给自己买一艘捕虾船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta buy me one of them shrimping boats, soon as I have some money.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.28,1:19:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在越南和巴巴说好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I made me a promise to Bubba in Vietnam
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.16,1:19:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等战争结束  我们就合伙捕虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that as soon as the war was over, we'd go in partners.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.77,1:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做捕虾船的船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'd be the captain of the shrimping boat
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.11,1:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当他的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'd be his first mate.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.43,1:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在他死了  我得担起船长的重任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But now that he's dead, that means I gotta be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.90,1:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-捕虾船的船长  -没错  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- A shrimp boat captain. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.73,1:19:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言既出  驷马难追  丹上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A promise is a promise, Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.12,1:19:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快听听啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now hear this!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.30,1:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等兵阿甘要当捕虾船的船长了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Private Gump here is gonna be a shrimp boat captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.71,1:19:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  吉利根{\fs12}[典出剧集《吉利根岛》]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I tell you what, Gilligan,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.26,1:19:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你当上捕虾船船长的那天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the day that you are a shrimp boat captain,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.94,1:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我来当你的大副  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I will come and be your first mate. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.31,1:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真能当上捕虾船船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're ever a shrimp boat captain,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.15,1:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我就当宇航员了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's the day I'm an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.09,1:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼  你在抱怨什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny, what are you complaining about?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.31,1:19:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在干什么  亲爱的  -轮椅帅哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What are you doing, hon? - Mr. Hot Wheels.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.82,1:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.02,1:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫弗里斯特  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My name is Forrest, Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.19,1:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是狡猾卡拉和长腿丽诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Cunning Carla and Long-Limbs Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.46,1:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了  甜心派\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, where you been, baby cakes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.16,1:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都没见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Haven't seen you around lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.81,1:20:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你圣诞节时真该来这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, you should have been here for Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.24,1:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为汤米请所有人喝了一轮酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause Tommy bought a round on the house
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.70,1:20:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给大家火鸡三明治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and gave everybody a turkey sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.30,1:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我有伴儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, well, I had company.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.19,1:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚刚就在那  时代广场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We was just there. That's at Times Square.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.41,1:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能不爱新年呢  你可以从头来过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't you just love New Year's? You get to start all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.74,1:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嘿  丽诺  -每个人都有第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, Lenore... - Everybody gets a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.03,1:20:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来有趣  在那欢乐的气氛之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's funny, but in the middle of all that fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.72,1:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始想念珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I began to think about Jenny,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.84,1:20:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着她会如何在加州度过新年夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wondering how she was spending her New Year's night out in California.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.96,1:20:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八  七  六  五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eight, seven, six, five,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.61,1:21:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四  三  二  一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}four, three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.21,1:21:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.47,1:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐  丹上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Happy New Year, Lieutenant Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.38,1:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么回事  是不是傻  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you, stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.57,1:22:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.78,1:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.10,1:22:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是打仗把鸡巴打没了还是怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you lose your pecker in the war or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.47,1:22:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你朋友是不是傻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What, is your friend stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.62,1:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.67,1:22:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你朋友是不是傻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I said, is your friend stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.89,1:22:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准说他傻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't call him stupid!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.71,1:22:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嘿  你别推她  -你闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, don't you push her! - You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.60,1:22:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-永远不准骂他傻  -怎么了  宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Don't you ever call him stupid! - What's the matter, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.98,1:22:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你为什么发这么大火  -给我滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Why are you so upset? - Just get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.07,1:22:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-蠢玩意儿  -拿好你们的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Stupid damn... - Get your goddamn clothes...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.25,1:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就该上瑞普利的《信不信由你》节目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You belong in Ripley's Believe It Or Not!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.68,1:22:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\pos(305,190)\bord0\fn微软雅黑}专门报道阐述奇闻怪象的节目\N有漫画书  广播  电视等多种形式
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.22,1:22:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给我滚出去  -你就该去马戏团作为怪胎表演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get the hell out of here! - You should be in a sideshow!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.28,1:22:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧  滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.72,1:22:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  丽诺  我们没必要受这气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Lenore. We don't need this shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.79,1:22:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.67,1:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你个智障  -废物  你个怪胎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You retard. - Loser. You freak.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.22,1:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.96,1:23:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉毁了你的新年前夜派对  丹上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry I ruined your New Year's Eve party, Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.58,1:23:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身上一股烟味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She tasted like cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.99,1:23:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜丹上尉觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess Lieutenant Dan figured
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.58,1:23:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事你无法改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there's some things you just can't change.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.60,1:23:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想让别人叫他瘸子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't want to be called crippled,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.27,1:23:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我不想让别人说我傻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just like I didn't want to be called stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.36,1:23:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐  阿甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Happy New Year, Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.84,1:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国国家乒乓队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The US Ping-Pong team
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.31,1:23:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日在总统办公室里与尼克松总统见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}met with President Nixon today at an Oval Office ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.60,1:23:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  几个月后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And wouldn't you know it? A few months later,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.62,1:24:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们邀请我和乒乓球队去白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they invited me and the Ping-Pong team to visit the White House.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.57,1:24:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我又去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I went, again.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.81,1:24:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我又见到了美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I met the President of the United States, again.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.48,1:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗里斯特·甘\N美国国家乒乓球队\N1971年最佳球员
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.96,1:24:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这次  他们没给我们安排豪华酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only, this time, they didn't get us rooms in a real fancy hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.99,1:24:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在首都玩的开心吗  年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, are you enjoying yourself in our nation's capital, young man?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.40,1:24:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  长官  -你们住在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Well, where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.68,1:24:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-埃伯特酒店  -不不  这可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's called the Hotel Ebbott. - Oh, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.31,1:24:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一个更好的酒店  崭新  非常现代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know of a much nicer hotel. It's brand-new, very modern.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.43,1:24:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让我的手下给你安排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll have my people take care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.91,1:24:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安保部  弗兰克·威尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Security, Frank Wills.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.26,1:24:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  先生  你最好派一位维修人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, sir, you might want to send a maintenance man
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.12,1:24:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到对面的办公室看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over to that office across the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.64,1:24:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯灭了 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The lights are off,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.60,1:24:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定是在找保险丝盒什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they must be looking for a fuse box or something,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.67,1:24:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们在用手电筒  闪的我睡不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause them flashlights, they're keeping me awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.62,1:24:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  先生  我去检查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, sir. I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.14,1:24:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thank you. - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.08,1:24:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.83,1:24:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz343.3\pos(190.151,136.158)}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs16\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H60A0BE&}水门饭店
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.56,1:24:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  我将于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Therefore, I shall resign
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.93,1:24:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午辞去总统一职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the presidency effective at noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.90,1:24:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副总统福特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vice President Ford
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.15,1:25:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将于同一时间宣誓就职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will be sworn in as president at that hour in this office.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.12,1:25:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尤记得在第二任期开始时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As I recall the high hopes for America
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.87,1:25:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对美国给予的厚望...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with which we began this second term...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.08,1:25:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘中士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sergeant Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.03,1:25:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在  长官  -稍息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes, sir! - As you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.37,1:25:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的退伍文件 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have your discharge papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.44,1:25:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的服役结束了  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your service is up, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.87,1:25:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意思是我不能再打乒乓球了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does this mean I can't play Ping-Pong no more?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.75,1:25:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再为军队打了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the Army it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.33,1:25:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And just like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.18,1:25:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在美国军队的服役生涯结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my service in the United States Army was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.43,1:25:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I went home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.87,1:26:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了  妈妈 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm home, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.70,1:26:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.78,1:26:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-露易丝  他回来了  -当我回家时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Louise, he's here. - Now, when I got home,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.43,1:26:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我浑然不知  但妈妈接待了许多客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had no idea, but Mama had had all sorts of visitors.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.55,1:26:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接待了许多客人  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've had all sorts of visitors, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.05,1:26:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都想让你用他们的乒乓器材\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody wants you to use their Ping-Pong stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.19,1:26:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人甚至留下一张2.5万美元的支票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One man even left a check for $25,000
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.94,1:26:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿意说你喜欢用他们的乒乓球拍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you'd be agreeable to saying you liked using their paddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.71,1:26:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妈妈  我只喜欢用我自己的拍子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, but, Mama, I only like using my own paddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.36,1:26:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好  露易丝小姐  -你好  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi, Miss Louise. - Hey, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.58,1:26:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.62,1:26:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这可是2.5万美元  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it's $25,000, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.30,1:26:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也许你可以握着试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought maybe you could hold it for a while,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.61,1:26:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看会不会慢慢喜欢上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}see if it grows on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.05,1:26:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你气色不错  弗里斯特  -这点我妈倒是没说错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, you look good, Forrest. - That Mama, she sure was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.07,1:26:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你气色很好  -事情的发展真是出人意料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You look real good. - It's funny how things work out.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.78,1:26:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在家没待多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't stay home for long,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.19,1:26:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我曾承诺过巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I'd made a promise to Bubba,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.15,1:26:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我总是努力信守承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I always try to keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.43,1:26:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我去了拜尤拉巴特里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I went on down to Bayou La Batre
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.11,1:26:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见巴巴的家人  相互认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to meet Bubba's family and make their introduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.81,1:27:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是疯子  还是单纯的傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you crazy, or just plain stupid?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.12,1:27:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有做傻事的才是傻子  布鲁太太\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stupid is as stupid does, Mrs. Blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.56,1:27:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我也去祭奠了一下巴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, of course, I paid my respect to Bubba himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.91,1:27:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}本杰明·巴福德·布鲁
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.91,1:27:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我们的巴巴
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.64,1:27:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  巴巴  是我  弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Bubba, it's me, Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.16,1:27:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你说过的一切  而且我都想好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember everything you said, and I got it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.00,1:27:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里有我赚的24562美元47美分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm taking the $24,562 and 47 cents that I got...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.92,1:27:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是花剩下的  我理了发  买了新西服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or, that's left after a new hair cut and a new suit,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.60,1:27:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带妈妈去吃了一顿豪华大餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I took Mama out to a real fancy dinner,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.57,1:27:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还买了车票和三瓶汽水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I bought a bus ticket and three Dr. Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.49,1:27:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.27,1:27:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是个傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.35,1:27:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有做傻事的才是傻子  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stupid is as stupid does, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.56,1:27:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这笔钱是我做广告赚的  我宣传说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's what's left after me saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.47,1:27:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"当我代表全美乒乓球队去中国打比赛时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"When I was in China on the All-America Ping-Pong team,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.69,1:27:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最爱的乒乓球拍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I just loved playing Ping-Pong
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.08,1:28:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我那「巧又轻」牌的球拍"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with my Flex-O-Light Ping-Pong paddle,"
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.57,1:28:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管大家都知道这不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which everybody knows isn't true,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.88,1:28:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妈妈说这是个小小的善意谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but Mama says it's just a little white lie
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.27,1:28:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会伤害到任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so it wouldn't hurt nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.00,1:28:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我把钱都用来买汽油  绳索和新网\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, anyway, I'm putting all that on gas, ropes and new nets
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.69,1:28:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及一艘全新的捕虾船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a brand-new shrimping boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.16,1:28:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴教过我他所知的一切关于捕虾的知识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Bubba had told me everything he knew about shrimping,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.47,1:28:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道我发现了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you know what I found out?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.31,1:28:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕虾太难了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shrimping is tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.02,1:28:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只捕到5只虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I only caught five.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来几只  你就能给自己做道鸡尾酒鲜虾了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A couple more, you could have yourself a cocktail.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.96,1:29:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想过给这船起名吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ever think about naming this old boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.45,1:29:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有船无名可不吉利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's bad luck to have a boat without a name.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.50,1:29:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前从没给船起过名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd never named a boat before,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.13,1:29:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只能想到一个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but there was only one I could think of,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.54,1:29:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上最美的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the most beautiful name in the wide world.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.49,1:29:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.84,1:29:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好久没有珍妮的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I hadn't heard from Jenny in a long while,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.71,1:29:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我经常想她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I thought about her a lot,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.32,1:29:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望无论她现在在做什么  都能让她快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I hoped that whatever she was doing made her happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.01,1:31:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无时不刻不想着珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought about Jenny all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.27,1:32:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹上尉  你来这里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.15,1:32:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来试试我的海洋腿{\fs12}[在船上平稳行走的能力]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, thought I'd try out my sea legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.12,1:32:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你没有腿  丹上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you ain't got no legs, Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.70,1:32:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.37,1:32:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我写信了  蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You wrote me a letter, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.71,1:32:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧  弗里斯特·甘船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, well. Captain Forrest Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.21,1:32:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须亲自来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to see this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.92,1:32:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过  如果你当上了捕虾船船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I told you if you were ever a shrimp boat captain
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.72,1:32:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就来做你的大副  我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I'd be your first mate. Well, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.47,1:32:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是个信守承诺的男人  -好棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I am a man of my word. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.11,1:33:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你别妄想我会叫你"长官"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But don't you be thinking that i'm going to be calling you "sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.86,1:33:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.24,1:33:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's my boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.96,1:33:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种预感  如果我们往正东方行驶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a feeling if we head due east,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.08,1:33:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会捕到虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll find some shrimp,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.59,1:33:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以左转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so take a left.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.71,1:33:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-左转  -哪边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Take a left! - Which way?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.72,1:33:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边  它们在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Over there! They're over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.51,1:33:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把舵扶稳了  左转  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get on the wheel and take a left! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.02,1:33:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿甘  你在干什么  左转  左左左\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gump, what are you doing? Take a left! Left!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.48,1:33:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们肯定能在那里捕捞到虾  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's where we're going to find those shrimp, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.78,1:33:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将在那里捕捞到虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's where we'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.83,1:34:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还是没虾  丹上尉  -好吧  我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Still no shrimp, Lieutenant Dan. - Okay, so I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.92,1:34:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要怎么做才能找到虾呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are we going to find them?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.38,1:34:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不你去祷告  把虾子盼来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, maybe you should just pray for shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.19,1:34:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我每周日都会去教堂做礼拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I went to church every Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.19,1:34:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候丹中尉也会去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes Lieutenant Dan came, too,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.44,1:34:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过祷告都是我一个人在做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though I think he left the praying up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.71,1:34:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有虾 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.30,1:34:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拜的那个上帝怎么还不显灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where the hell's this God of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.92,1:34:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉这么说真的挺好笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's funny Lieutenant Dan said that,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.63,1:34:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他话音刚落  上帝就显灵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause right then, God showed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.57,1:35:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别想沉掉这艘船  -当时我害怕极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You'll never sink this boat! - Now, me, I was scared,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.41,1:35:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是丹中尉像发疯了一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but Lieutenant Dan, he was mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.83,1:35:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.29,1:35:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也叫暴风雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You call this a storm?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.00,1:35:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来啊  王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.59,1:35:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个是时候决一死战了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's time for a showdown! You and me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.01,1:35:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这  来打败我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm right here! Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.81,1:35:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想弄沉这艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll never sink this boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.69,1:35:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风卡门于昨日席卷该地区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hurricane Carmen came through here yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.78,1:35:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎摧毁了沿途的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}destroying nearly everything in its path.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.49,1:35:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而说到沿海的其他小镇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And as in other towns up and down the coast,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.20,1:36:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜尤拉巴特里的整个虾行业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bayou La Batre's entire shrimping industry
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.66,1:36:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因飓风卡门而遭到重创  损失惨重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has fallen victim to Carmen and has been left in utter ruin.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.70,1:36:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位记者采访了当地官员后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Speaking with local officials, this reporter has learned,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.87,1:36:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知仅有一艘捕虾船幸免于难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in fact, only one shrimping boat actually survived the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.79,1:36:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露易丝  快看  是弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Louise. Louise, there's Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.09,1:36:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后  捕虾变得轻而易举\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After that, shrimping was easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.72,1:36:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为大家还是需要虾来做鸡尾酒鲜虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Since people still needed them shrimps for shrimp cocktails
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.10,1:36:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有烧烤什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and barbecues and all,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.56,1:36:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上只剩下了我们这么一艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we were the only boat left standing,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.23,1:36:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就只能靠巴巴甘虾业了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba-Gump Shrimp's what they got.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.73,1:36:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之后又采购了许多船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got a whole bunch of boats,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.99,1:36:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12艘珍妮号  还有个老旧的大仓库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}12 Jennys, a big old warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.07,1:36:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还专门定做了印有"巴巴甘"品牌名的帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We even have hats that say "Bubba-Gump" on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.16,1:36:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴甘虾业  家喻户晓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bubba-Gump Shrimp. It's a household name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.91,1:36:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hold on there, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.41,1:36:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在告诉我 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you telling me
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.63,1:36:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是巴巴甘虾业的老板吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're the owner of the Bubba-Gump Shrimp Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.04,1:36:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们挣的钱比大卫·克洛科特还多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir. We got more money than Davy Crockett.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.88,1:36:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  我这辈子没少听人吹牛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy, I heard some whoppers in my time,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.97,1:37:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你这绝对是最扯的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but that tops them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.60,1:37:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们竟然和百万富翁坐一张凳子上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We was sitting next to a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.81,1:37:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你的故事非常精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I thought it was a very lovely story,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.86,1:37:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲得很生动  激情澎湃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you tell it so well, with such enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.28,1:37:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看看丹中尉长什么样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like to see what Lieutenant Dan looks like?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.95,1:37:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, yes, I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.75,1:37:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's him right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.97,1:37:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz354.7\pos(108.809,95.525)}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H2E3A2A&}财富
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.92,1:37:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说啊  丹中尉这个人...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And let me tell you something about Lieutenant Dan...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.42,1:37:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.80,1:37:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未感谢你救了我一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never thanked you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.75,1:38:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的确从未开口谢过我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He never actually said so,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.17,1:38:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得他已经和上帝重归于好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I think he made his peace with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.10,1:38:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是17天以来的第二次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the second time in 17 days,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.02,1:38:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福特总统今天逃过了一起潜在的暗杀行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}President Ford escaped possible assassination today.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.51,1:38:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部呼叫珍妮一号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Base to Jenny 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.85,1:38:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部呼叫珍妮一号  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Base to Jenny 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.78,1:38:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是珍妮一号  请说  玛格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny 1. Go, Margo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.40,1:38:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来电找弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest has a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.07,1:38:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  跟那个人说回头再打过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, you'll have to tell them to call him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.53,1:38:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他现在没空  -他妈妈病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He is indisposed at the moment. - His mama's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.80,1:39:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-妈妈在哪儿  -在楼上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where's Mama? - She's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.06,1:39:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.89,1:39:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我明天再来  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll see you tomorrow. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.07,1:39:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能站得笔直的了啊  小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We sure got you straightened out, didn't we, boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.71,1:39:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the matter, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.00,1:39:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要死了  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm dying, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.84,1:39:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来  坐这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on in, sit down over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.57,1:40:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么快要死了  妈妈 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you dying, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.04,1:40:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的时候到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's my time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.20,1:40:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是时候到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just my time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.66,1:40:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.00,1:40:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't you be afraid, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.29,1:40:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡只是人生的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Death is just a part of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.67,1:40:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人终有一死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}something we're all destined to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.05,1:40:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前不知道  但我注定要做你的妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't know it, but I was destined to be your mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.34,1:40:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也尽了全力  -你做得很好  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I did the best I could. - You did good, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.48,1:40:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信一个人的命运该由自己创造\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I happen to believe you make your own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.44,1:40:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好利用上帝赋予你的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have to do the best with what God gave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.53,1:40:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命运是什么  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's my destiny, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.78,1:40:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就得由你自己慢慢领悟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're going to have to figure that out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.33,1:40:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活就像一盒巧克力  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Life is a box of chocolates, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.46,1:41:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不知道你将得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You never know what you're going to get.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.71,1:41:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈总是有办法把事情解释得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama always had a way of explaining things
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.13,1:41:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也能听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I could understand them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.09,1:41:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想你的  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will miss you, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.13,1:41:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她患了癌症  然后在一个礼拜二去世\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She had got the cancer and died on a Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.85,1:41:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给她买了一顶碎花帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bought her a new hat with little flowers on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.15,1:41:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这事  我要说的就这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's all I have to say about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.16,1:41:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说你在等7路公交车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't you say you were waiting for the number seven bus?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.70,1:41:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  下一班很快就到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There'll be another one along shortly.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.08,1:41:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我当过橄榄球明星  战争英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, because I had been a football star, and a war hero,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.96,1:41:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国名人  捕虾船船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a national celebrity, and a shrimping boat captain,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.76,1:41:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及大学生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a college graduate,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.80,1:41:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉巴马州绿弓县的市议员们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.97,1:41:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同商量后  决定给我一份好工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}decided to get together and offered me a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.68,1:41:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  我没再回去给丹中尉工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I never went back to work for Lieutenant Dan,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.35,1:42:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他确实在好好帮我理财\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though he did take care of my Bubba-Gump money.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.10,1:42:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给我投资了一家水果公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He got me invested in some kind of fruit company.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.77,1:42:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(143.142,156.832)\frz38.99}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H7C7C86&}苹果电脑公司
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.82,1:42:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来  他打电话告诉我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so then, I got a call from him saying
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.49,1:42:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再也不用操心没钱用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we don't have to worry about money no more,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.20,1:42:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回答说  "挺好的  少个烦心事"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I said, "That's good. One less thing."
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.37,1:42:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈常说一个人不需要太多财富\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Mama said there's only so much fortune a man really needs,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.00,1:42:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多出来的只是为了显摆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the rest is just for showing off.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.96,1:42:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就把一大笔钱捐给了正方福音教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I gave a whole bunch of it to the Foursquare gospel church,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.50,1:42:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿甘医疗中心
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.59,1:42:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还捐了一大笔钱给拜尤拉巴特里渔业医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I gave a whole bunch to the Bayou La Batre Fishing Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.27,1:42:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然巴巴不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And even though Bubba was dead
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.18,1:42:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉说我这么做简直是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Lieutenant Dan said I was nuts,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.06,1:42:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把巴巴的股份转给了他妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gave Bubba's mama Bubba's share.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.86,1:42:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.65,1:42:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她再也不用给别人家当佣人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't have to work in nobody's kitchen no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.99,1:42:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That smells wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.41,1:43:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有用不完的钱  而且非常喜欢这一行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And 'cause I was a gazillionaire and I liked doing it so much,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.41,1:43:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都是免费除草的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I cut that grass for free.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.38,1:43:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当夜晚来临  无所事事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But at night time when there was nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.34,1:43:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里空荡荡的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the house was all empty,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.72,1:43:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会想起珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd always think of Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.91,1:44:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来有一天  她回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then, she was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.15,1:44:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.28,1:45:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.84,1:45:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮回来后  跟我住在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny came back and stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.05,1:45:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是她无处可去了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe it was because she had nowhere else to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.84,1:45:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是她筋疲力尽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or maybe it was because she was so tired,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.10,1:45:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她睡了好久好久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause she went to bed and slept and slept,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.10,1:45:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟好几年没睡过觉似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like she hadn't slept in years.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.89,1:45:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能回家我真的很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was wonderful having her home.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.52,1:45:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每天都会出门散步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every day we'd take a walk
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.52,1:45:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像树上的猴子一样喋喋不休\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'd jabber on like a monkey in a tree,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.65,1:45:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她静静地听我说着关于打乒乓球  捕虾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she'd listen about Ping-Ponging, and shrimping,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.24,1:45:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妈妈去天堂的各种经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Mama making a trip up to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.87,1:45:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我一个人在说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.66,1:45:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮大多数时候都一言不发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny most of the time was real quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.16,1:46:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.28,1:47:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我觉得  石头都不够她砸的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes I guess there just aren't enough rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.92,1:47:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没搞懂过她为什么回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never really knew why she came back,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.25,1:47:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.63,1:47:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就像回到了从前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was like olden times.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.51,1:47:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又变得形影不离了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We was like peas and carrots again.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.88,1:47:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都会摘下鲜花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every day, I'd pick pretty flowers
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.26,1:47:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装点她的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and put them in her room for her,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.81,1:47:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也送了我一件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she gave me the best gift
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.06,1:47:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界最好的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}anyone could ever get in the wide world.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.81,1:47:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一双新鞋  -这是专业跑步鞋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- New shoes. - They make them just for running.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.40,1:47:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还教我怎么跳舞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she even showed me how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.00,1:47:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮和我  就像一家人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, well, we was like family, Jenny and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.67,1:48:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我人生中最幸福的时光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it was the happiest time in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.32,1:48:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的独立日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...and this Fourth is witnessing
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.24,1:48:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举办了全国最为盛大的焰火晚会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one of the largest fireworks displays in the nation's...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.32,1:48:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你看完了吗  -就在纽约港\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You done watching it? - ...here in New York Harbor...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.48,1:48:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上床睡觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.79,1:48:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由女神像...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Statue of Liberty...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.42,1:48:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁给我好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.26,1:48:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会是个好丈夫的  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd make a good husband, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.77,1:48:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You would, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.73,1:49:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不愿意嫁给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you won't marry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.32,1:49:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想娶我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't want to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.07,1:49:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不爱我  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you love me, Jenny?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.58,1:49:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然不够聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not a smart man,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.29,1:49:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道什么是爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I know what love is.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.79,1:50:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.04,1:50:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我是爱你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, I do love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.64,1:51:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是要逃去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you running off to?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.31,1:51:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这不是要逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not running.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.90,1:52:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  没有缘由地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That day, for no particular reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.56,1:52:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定出去跑一圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I decided to go for a little run.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.31,1:52:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我跑到了路的尽头 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I ran to the end of the road,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.17,1:52:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我跑到那里时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and when I got there,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.82,1:52:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着要不跑到镇子的另一头去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought maybe I'd run to the end of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.63,1:52:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特总统由于中暑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}President Carter, suffering from heat exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.24,1:52:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跌入了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}fell into the arms of...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.01,1:52:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我跑到那里后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when I got there,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.81,1:52:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想着干脆横穿绿弓县吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought maybe I'd just run across Greenbow County.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.01,1:53:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我想既然已经跑了这么远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I figured since I'd run this far,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.50,1:53:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如就跑遍整个阿拉巴马州吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}maybe I'd just run across the great state of Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.47,1:53:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}欢迎来到密西西比州
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.94,1:53:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.73,1:53:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑步横穿了阿拉巴马州\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ran clear across Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.72,1:53:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有缘由  我就一直向前跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For no particular reason, I just kept on going.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.06,1:53:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直跑到了大海边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ran clear to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.47,1:53:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}圣莫尼卡
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.54,1:53:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我到达那里时  心想都跑这么远了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when I got there, I figured since I'd gone this far,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.37,1:53:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如调个头继续跑下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}might as well turn around and just keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.97,1:53:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我抵达另一个大洋时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when I got to another ocean,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.38,1:53:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心想既然都到这了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I figured since I'd gone this far,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.31,1:53:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如转过身  再继续跑下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I might as well just turn back and keep right on going.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.98,1:53:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑累了就睡  饿了就吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I got tired, I slept. When I got hungry, I ate.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.14,1:53:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要方便的时候  你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I had to go, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.71,1:53:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去方便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I went.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.96,1:53:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你一直都在跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so, you just ran.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.81,1:53:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.12,1:54:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路我想了很多有关妈妈  巴巴和丹中尉的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd think a lot about Mama and Bubba and Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.36,1:54:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我主要还是在想珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But most of all, I thought about Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.99,1:54:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老是会想起她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought about her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.94,1:54:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在两年多的时间里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For more than two years now,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.45,1:54:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位名叫弗里斯特·甘的男子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a man named Forrest Gump,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.08,1:54:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉巴马州绿弓县的一位园丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a gardener from Greenbow, Alabama,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.26,1:54:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了停下来睡觉之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stopping only to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.53,1:54:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑遍了整个美国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has been running across America.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.84,1:54:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看查尔斯·库珀带来的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Charles Cooper brings us this report.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.70,1:55:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第四次跑遍全美的旅行中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the fourth time on his journey across America,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.12,1:55:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特·甘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest Gump,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.92,1:55:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉巴马州绿弓县的一位园丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the gardener from Greenbow, Alabama,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.16,1:55:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将于今日再次穿越密西西比河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is about to cross the Mississippi River again today.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.62,1:55:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的天呐  弗里斯特  -先生  你为什么要跑步呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll be damned. Forrest? - Sir, why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.90,1:55:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跑步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.95,1:55:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了宣扬世界和平吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you doing this for world peace?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.72,1:55:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是为了那些流浪汉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you doing this for the homeless?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.16,1:55:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了妇女权利而跑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you running for women's rights?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.02,1:55:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是为了环保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or for the environment?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.15,1:55:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是动物保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or for animals?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.21,1:55:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They just couldn't believe
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.39,1:55:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有人不为任何原因跑遍全国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that somebody would do all that running for no particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.64,1:55:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.69,1:55:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just felt like running.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.26,1:55:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just felt like running.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.04,1:55:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你  没想到真的是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's you. I can't believe it's really you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.93,1:55:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在  不知怎么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.76,1:55:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人似乎能够理解我的行为了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what I was doing seemed to make sense to people.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.19,1:55:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉  就像脑袋突然开窍了一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it was like an alarm went off in my head, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.42,1:55:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  「这家伙是个积极振作的人」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I said, "Here's a guy that's got his act together.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.40,1:55:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「这家伙参透了一切」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Here's somebody who's got it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.42,1:55:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「这家伙知晓人生答案」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Here's somebody who has the answer."
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.72,1:55:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你去哪里  我都跟着你  甘先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll follow you anywhere, Mr. Gump.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.60,1:55:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就有人跟着我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I got company.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.48,1:55:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  有了更多的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And after that, I got more company.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.75,1:56:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再然后  更多的人加入了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then, even more people joined in.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.59,1:56:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来有人跟我说  这能给人希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody later told me it gave people hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.62,1:56:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我对此倒是不是很明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now... Now, I don't know anything about that,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.65,1:56:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中有些人问我能不能帮助他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but some of those people asked me if I could help them out.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.47,1:56:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  老兄  不知道能不能请你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, man, hey, listen, I was wondering if you might help me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.90,1:56:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我是生产车尾贴的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, I'm in the bumper sticker business
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.67,1:56:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在努力想出一条好标语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I've been trying to think up a good slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.47,1:56:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你如此激励人心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And since you have been such a big inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.69,1:56:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带动了这里的很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the people around here,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.75,1:56:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着  也许你能帮我想一个标语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought you might be able to help me jump into...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.81,1:56:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  你刚刚跑过了一堆狗屎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whoa, man! You just ran through a big pile of dog shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.94,1:56:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这很正常  -什么  狗屎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It happens. - What, shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.09,1:56:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.09,1:56:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年后  我听说那家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And some years later, I heard that that fellow
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.72,1:56:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的想到了一条出色的车尾贴标语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}did come up with a bumper sticker slogan,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.61,1:56:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还因此赚了很多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he made a lot of money off of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.77,1:56:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}屎属正常
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.07,1:56:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一次  跑步的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Another time, I was running along,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.34,1:56:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说他的T恤生意赔光了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}somebody who had lost all his money in the T-shirt business,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.84,1:56:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想把我的脸印在T恤上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he wanted to put my face on a T-shirt,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.81,1:57:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他画画不好  又没有相机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he couldn't draw that well, and he didn't have a camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.08,1:57:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  用这个  反正也没人喜欢这个颜色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here, use this one. Nobody likes that color anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.31,1:57:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.77,1:57:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多年后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, some years later,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.92,1:57:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现那个人为T恤想到了好的创意图案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found out that that man did come up with an idea for a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.79,1:57:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因此赚了很多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He made a lot of money off of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.97,1:57:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  就像我说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, like I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.94,1:57:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人陪着我同行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had a lot of company.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.81,1:57:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈生前常说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mama always said,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.96,1:57:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「要想向前走  就得先放下过去」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You got to put the past behind you before you can move on."
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.95,1:57:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是我跑步的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I think that's what my running was all about.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.21,1:57:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑了三年  两个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had run for three years, two months,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.42,1:57:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加14天16小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}14 days and 16 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.30,1:58:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静  安静  他要说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Quiet. Quiet. He's going to say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.23,1:58:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.77,1:58:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.54,1:58:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.78,1:58:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And just like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.63,1:58:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的跑步生涯结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my running days was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.99,1:58:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我回到了阿拉巴马的家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I went home to Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.54,1:58:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才  下午2:25\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Moments ago, at 2:25 P.M.,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.10,1:58:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里根总统正要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as President Reagan was leaving the...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.58,1:59:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五六次枪击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...five or six gunshots
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.08,1:59:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑刺客身份未知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}were fired by an unknown would-be assassin.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.09,1:59:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统胸部中枪  刺客...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The President was shot in the chest, and the assailant...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.66,1:59:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你收了邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I picked up the mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.19,1:59:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天  非常突然地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And one day, out of the blue clear sky,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.41,1:59:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了来自珍妮的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got a letter from Jenny,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.34,1:59:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她问我能不能去萨凡纳看望她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wondering if I could come down to Savannah and see her,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.52,1:59:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that's what I'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.34,1:59:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在电视上看到我跑步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She saw me on TV, running.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.98,1:59:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该坐9号公交车去里士满街\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm supposed to go on the number nine bus to Richmond Street
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.27,1:59:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车  走一个街区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and get off and go one block
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.02,1:59:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左转去亨利街1947号  4号公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}left to 1947 Henry Street, Apartment 4.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.38,1:59:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不用坐公交车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why, you don't need to take a bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.07,1:59:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往那个方向走五六个街区就能到亨利街\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Henry Street is just five or six blocks down that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.35,1:59:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那边吗  -就是那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Down that way? - Down that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.82,1:59:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴和你聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.64,1:59:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你一切顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope everything works out for you!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.20,2:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.20,2:00:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.83,2:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进  请进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come in, come in!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.47,2:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了你的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got your letter.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.74,2:00:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想你有没有收到呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was wondering about that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.02,2:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this your house?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.68,2:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  有点乱  我刚下班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's messy right now. I just got off work.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.94,2:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.23,2:00:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这里还有空调呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.72,2:00:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -我吃掉了一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thank you. - I ate some.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.44,2:00:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我留了一本你的剪报和其他材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I kept a scrapbook of your clippings and everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.96,2:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord0\an8\pos(293.678,43.485)\frz352\fn方正小标宋_GBK\c&H77C3D1&}跑步者的世界
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.00,2:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.28,2:00:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  你跑步的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this, I got you running.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.83,2:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H419050&\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}夜店舞女表示
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.83,2:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H419050&}弗里斯特·甘让我做他的秘密情人
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.85,2:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz330.3\pos(336.99,158.97)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs14\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我不认识她
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.56,2:00:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑了好远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ran a long way,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.29,2:00:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑了很久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.33,2:00:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And there...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.32,2:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  弗里斯特  我不知道该怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, Forrest, I don't know how to say this.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.41,2:01:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为我对你的所作所为道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just I want to apologize for anything that I ever did to you,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.59,2:01:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我迷失了很久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause I was messed up for a long time, and...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.65,2:01:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.62,2:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这位是阿拉巴马来的老朋友  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is an old friend from Alabama. - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.04,2:01:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  下周我换了班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, next week my schedule changes,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.74,2:01:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就可以...但是谢谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I'll be able to... But thanks...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.88,2:01:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我要走了  珍  我把车靠着别人的车停了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem. Got to go, Jen, I'm double-parked.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.13,2:01:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  谢谢  -再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Okay. Thanks. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.25,2:01:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的好朋友  甘先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my very good friend, Mr. Gump.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.97,2:01:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他打个招呼好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you say hi to him?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.25,2:01:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好  甘先生  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hello, Mr. Gump. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.44,2:01:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我能去看电视了吗  -好  但要小声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can I go watch TV now? - Yes, you can. Just keep it low.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.12,2:01:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你当妈妈了  珍妮  -我当妈妈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're a mama, Jenny. - I'm a mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.43,2:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His name's Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.40,2:02:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.26,2:02:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用他父亲的名字给他起名的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I named him after his daddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.51,2:02:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他父亲也叫弗里斯特吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He got a daddy named Forrest, too?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.22,2:02:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是他父亲  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're his daddy, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.01,2:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  看着我  看着我  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, look at me. Look at me, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.57,2:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不需要做  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's nothing you need to do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.02,2:02:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有做错任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.24,2:02:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.93,2:02:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很漂亮  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't he beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.91,2:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我见过的最漂亮的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's the most beautiful thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.69,2:02:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.38,2:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他聪明吗  还是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is he smart, or...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.31,2:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很聪明  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's very smart.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.61,2:03:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是他们班上最聪明的一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's one of the smartest in his class.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.70,2:03:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  去和他说说话吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it's okay. Go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.57,2:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在看什么  -伯特和厄尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What are you watching? - Bert and Ernie.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.51,2:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  我病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:01.95,2:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你感冒了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What, do you have a cough due to a cold?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.53,2:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感染上了一种病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have some kind of virus,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.09,2:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生们  他们不知道是什么病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the doctors don't... They don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.87,2:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也没办法治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there isn't anything they can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.25,2:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以和我回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You could come home with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.25,2:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮  你和小弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny, you and little Forrest
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.13,2:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和我一起住在绿弓县\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}could come stay at my house in Greenbow.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.23,2:04:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是病了  我可以照顾你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll take care of you if you're sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.46,2:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意娶我吗  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you marry me, Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.20,2:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.19,2:04:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请入座\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.90,2:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  该开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest? It's time to start.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.88,2:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的领带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your tie.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.08,2:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.93,2:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.71,2:05:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.96,2:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你换上新腿了  新腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got new legs. New legs!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.90,2:06:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我有新腿了  专门定制的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I got new legs. Custom-made.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.33,2:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钛合金的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Titanium alloy.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.58,2:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用来造航空飞船的材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's what they use on the space shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.46,2:06:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Magic legs.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.85,2:06:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的未婚妻  苏珊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my fiancee, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.88,2:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.59,2:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.37,2:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹中尉  这是我的珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lieutenant Dan, this is my Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.09,2:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.50,2:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴终于见到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's nice to meet you finally.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.32,2:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你愿意接受珍妮做你的妻子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you, Forrest, take Jenny to be your wife?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.39,2:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮  你愿意接受弗里斯特做你的丈夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you, Jenny, take Forrest to be your husband?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.90,2:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宣布你们结为夫妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so I pronounce you man and wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.61,2:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  弗里斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.86,2:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在越南的时候你怕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Were you scared in Vietnam?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.26,2:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.89,2:07:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.48,2:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候雨停得足够久  就能看到星星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes it would stop raining long enough for the stars to come out.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.51,2:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种时候还好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.93,2:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像太阳要睡觉前的海湾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was like just before the sun goes to bed down on the bayou.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.15,2:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海面总有无数光芒闪烁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was always a million sparkles on the water.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.67,2:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像天池  特别清澈  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like that mountain lake. It was so clear, Jenny,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.83,2:08:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就像有两个天空  一个扣在另一个上面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it looked like there were two skies, one on top of the other.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.99,2:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有在沙漠  当太阳升起时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then, in the desert, when the sun comes up,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.45,2:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都无法分辨  天与地的交接处是在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't tell where heaven stopped and the earth began.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.02,2:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太美了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.44,2:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望当时我能和你一起欣赏这些美景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish I could've been there with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.61,2:09:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.78,2:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.58,2:09:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在一个周六的清晨去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You died on a Saturday morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.86,2:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你安葬在了我们的树下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I had you placed here under our tree.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.25,2:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你父亲的房子推平了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I had that house of your father's bulldozed to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.18,2:09:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.04,2:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总说死亡是人生的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}always said that dying was a part of life.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.34,2:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(134.691,83.406)}{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H606065&}珍妮·甘
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.37,2:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sure wish it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.31,2:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弗里斯特过得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Little Forrest is doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.55,2:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.89,2:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很快又要开始上学了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About to start school again soon,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.19,2:10:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都给他做早餐  午餐  晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I make his breakfast, lunch and dinner every day.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.41,2:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天确保他梳头  刷牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I make sure he combs his hair and brushes his teeth every day.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.48,2:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教他怎么打乒乓球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Teaching him how to play Ping-Pong.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.45,2:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.58,2:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's really good.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.80,2:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗里斯特  你来发球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forrest, you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.30,2:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们经常钓鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We fish a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.48,2:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天晚上我们都读书  他好聪明  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And every night, we read a book. He's so smart, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.08,2:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会为他骄傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd be so proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.01,2:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为他骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.68,2:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给你写了一封信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wrote you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.33,2:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我不能看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he says I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.79,2:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能看  所以就留给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not supposed to, so I'll just leave it here for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.00,2:11:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(146.311,147.564)}{\fn手书体\fs20\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H868689&}给妈妈
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.15,2:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jenny,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.20,2:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道妈妈说的对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know if Mama was right,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.75,2:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者丹中尉说的对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or if it's Lieutenant Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.19,2:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.01,2:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是每个人都有宿命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if we each have a destiny,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.61,2:11:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们只是像风一般飘摇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or if we're all just floating around accidental-like on a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.21,2:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I think
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.97,2:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许二者皆有吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}maybe it's both.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.06,2:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许两种情况是同时发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe both is happening at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.12,2:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很想你  珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I miss you, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.49,2:12:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有什么需要  我就在不远处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If there's anything you need, I won't be far away.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.08,2:13:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的校车来了 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here's your bus.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.51,2:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.57,2:13:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这本书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know this.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.17,2:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拿去班上做展示演讲  因为...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna show that for show-and-tell because
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.26,2:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶曾给你念过这本书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grandma used to read it to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.00,2:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My favorite book.
